{"tid":454441,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 後門貨價曝光 回收價必再調低！","createTime":"2017-11-01T06:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T07:44:57.000Z","uid":64181,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80dadc50a8049f0ba6ae9a5b9a566b1bcf866d9a","tid":454441,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"iPhone X 後日正式開售，「公司貨」未有像 iPhone 8 般提早 1 星期開盤，今日終於有盤口開出。有「公司」向先達收機舖報價，炒價似乎比先前預期再低！<br />\n<br />\n消息人士向 <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6616eca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者透露，「公司貨」價 64GB 報 HK$12,800，256GB 部 HK$13,800，暫時兩色同價，11 月 3 日可以交貨，價格未有像預期高，而回收價預計再比此價低 HK$500 至 HK$1,000。不過，去年 iPhone 7 Plus JetBlack 256GB 版，「公司貨」價起初也報 HK$15,000，但於開售第 2 日，「公司貨」缺貨，先達回收價升到 HK$20,000 港元，故此也視乎大陸、外地需求是否強勁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1935000/1937413/iPhoneXBackdoorPrice1Nov02_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1935000%2F1937413%2FiPhoneXBackdoorPrice1Nov02_600.jpeg&h=df56f7fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所謂「公司貨」又或「後門貨」，是有 Apple 銷售夥伴，直接向先達回收商批發，而每家「公司」的報價可能也不一樣，而且經常變動。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6616eca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>"},{"pid":"5e40e161295768ff46070fdfa967b74a34e4ff42","tid":454441,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0089b934430c91294b23cf61b14a6a1f3c6ee66","tid":454441,"uid":35966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"Strong hold 到聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"